Marco Fuser (born 9 March 1991) is an Italian rugby union player who plays as a Lock.  He currently plays for Benetton in the Pro14.In May 2012, Fuser was called up by the Italian national rugby union team against Canada. On 14 June, he made his international debut for Italy against Canada.


